              'Training and awareness programs for employees and high-risk roles',
              'A whistle-blower system with clear investigation, sanction, and authority-reporting processes',
              'Internal controls against counterfeiting, piracy, and IP theft',
              'Transparent reporting on outcomes',
              'Regular review and improvement based on metrics and feedback',
            ],
          },
          {
            intro: 'To go beyond baseline:',
            items: [
              'Adopt the policies organization-wide (not just project-wide)',
              'Adopt the Supplier Code of Conduct organization-wide',
              'Communicate policy expectations clearly to business partners and value-chain entities (RFPs, vendor contracts, etc.)',
